Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:24.29,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Felt-sama, thank you for gracing us \Nwith your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.06,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Reinhard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:34.98,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:38.43,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You dragged me here with no explanation, \Nand what do you call all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.75,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's brought on such behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:46.01,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Don't block my kick and ask me \Nthat, like nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:48.19,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I've had just about all I can take!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:51.05,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Does the dress not suit your taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:52.76,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,It looks lovely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:55.79,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about the dress, \Nand I'm not embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:57.91,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's the girl from...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it isn't that easy to change \Nsomeone at their core...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And not only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:06.54,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:09.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's been a while. \NHow have you be—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:10.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Randaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:13.88,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the hole in your gut \Nisn't bothering you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:16.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you were worried about that, \Nbe nice to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:19.83,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Felt-sama, if you have finished \Nrekindling old friendships,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:21.31,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,please step over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:26.08,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is it you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:29.53,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to say, \N"To act more like a lady,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:31.05,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,but this comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:42.83,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the dragon gem has recognized \NFelt-sama as a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:49.63,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,With her participation approved,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:54.08,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it is time to begin the \Nroyal selection in earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:01.02,Default,Rickert,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Dragon Stone has recognized her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:04.01,Default,Rickert,0000,0000,0000,,isn't her selection a bit problematic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:07.07,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,You believe we, the Imperial Knights, \Nhave made an error?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:12.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere's getting kind of dicey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:15.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:18.03,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}nyo{\i0} big deal to me, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:22.78,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I've already pledged my \Nloyalty exclusively to one lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.24,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.71,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,My sword already belongs to Anastasia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:35.38,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my feelings for Emilia won't \Ncome in second to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:39.12,Default,Guy1,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have the self-awareness \Nto become a ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.54,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You can dress her up, but you \Ncan't give her grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:40.84,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,She's uneducated, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:42.80,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:45.89,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,Knight Reinhard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:51.94,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,would you begin by explaining to us \Nwhat led you to her discovery?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:58.69,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I took custody of Felt-sama in the slums, \Nabout one month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:02.06,Default,Rickert,0000,0000,0000,,She's a gutter rat from the slums?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:05.16,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sorry for being a gutter rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.52,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You were the ones who dragged \Nme here against my will!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:11.95,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,All of this long-winded blather \Ncould not be more tedious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.56,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I suppose you lived as a gutter rat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.87,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,because you could only manage \Ntedious conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:20.26,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? If you want a fight, you've got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:21.92,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,What insolence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, that isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.94,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Many pardons, Priscilla-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.52,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking,\N in a hallowed place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:38.94,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,I was only trying to teach an \Nuntrained little bitch her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.69,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:46.97,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,Then, will you also apologize for being born?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:49.38,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,You silver-haired half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.00,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I have no connection to the witch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, could you drop it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one to suffer if you \Nmake too many enemies, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:02.60,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all quite finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.89,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Then, royal selection candidates, \Nplease come forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.87,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Priscilla Barielle-sama and her attendant, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.38,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,This selection is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.19,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one suited to rule this nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:19.36,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to do is serve \Nme and grovel at my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:23.32,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Head of the Karsten family, \NCrusch Karsten-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.70,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,and her attendant, the knight Felix Argyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:29.37,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Should I become the new ruler,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.33,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I will make the dragon forget \Nthe covenant it demanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.85,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon's Empire of Lugunica \Nbelongs not to the dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.76,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Anastasia Hoshin-sama,\Nof the Hoshin Company,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:44.27,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,and her attendant, the knight Julius Euclius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:48.16,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a greedy gal, so I want everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.56,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,No amount of commercial \Nsuccess can satisfy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:53.89,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,I want my own nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:57.33,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-sama and the man endorsing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Margrave Roswaal L. Mathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:02.19,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I have only one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For all to be equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.75,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I desire to create a nation where \Nall citizens are equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:13.88,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Still, after the introduction of \Nall those knightly attendants,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:17.62,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,I feel terribly out of place here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:20.54,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, Felt-sama and her attendant,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the knight Reinhard van Astrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.16,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on! Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:28.44,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I'd be the next ruler...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.39,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd want to be in a royal selection?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:34.21,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you withdraw\Nfrom the selection?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.10,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.87,Default,Rickert,0000,0000,0000,,This is a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.55,Default,Rickert,0000,0000,0000,,I've overlooked this because\Nthe situation is dire,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.73,Default,Rickert,0000,0000,0000,,but to drag it out this long is senseless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.30,Default,Bordeaux,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Astrea family offers\Na gutter rat to rule us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.80,Default,Bordeaux,0000,0000,0000,,while Margrave Mathers endorses \Na half-devil? Utter foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:53.70,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't at all nice to call\Na half-elf a "half-devil."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.46,Default,Bordeaux,0000,0000,0000,,That silver-haired half-devil
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:06:00.29,Default,Bordeaux,0000,0000,0000,,matches the Jealous Witch's appearance, \Nas described for generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:04.38,Default,Bordeaux,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you not realize that even allowing \Nher in the throne room is dreadful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:06.21,Default,Bordeaux,0000,0000,0000,,Filthy woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:10.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.46,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, it's all right! Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I will not stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You people are full of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to Emilia—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:24.27,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:30.95,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to formally introduce myself \Nto the honored council of elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.13,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:36.77,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I am accompanied by Puck, a great \Nspirit who controls fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.62,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,and I am a silver-haired half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.02,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,A great spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.67,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that my half-elf lineage,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:48.62,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,and other similarities to the witch, \Nsubject me to prejudice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:49.34,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:56.60,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I adamantly refuse to let all my potential \Nbe plucked out simply for that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.52,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:05.08,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,What, exactly, is that young man's position?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:07.66,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um, well, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:11.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Emilia. I've made up my mind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.60,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Your mind? To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.70,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Subaru, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:17.16,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:22.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, members of \Nthe council of elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Natsuki Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:27.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I am a manservant in Roswaal's mansion, \Nand I serve as this candidate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-sama's best knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.82,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, a knight, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:41.48,Default,Roswaal,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he knows little of our world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.01,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for interrupting,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:47.82,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but there is something I must ask him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:52.26,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly proclaim yourself \Nto be Emilia-sama's knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:55.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:08:00.08,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You just declared that you are a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:05.04,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And you did so here, audaciously, \Nbefore the Knights of Lugunica!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:10.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty well-coordinated...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys practice that for this meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.83,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make known to all the\Ndignity of our empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.26,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,we are highly conscious of \Nour identities every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:23.69,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the resolve to match that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make Emilia-sama the ruler...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will make her the ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:33.86,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And you believe you have the \Nresolve and strength for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything as grand as resolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm well aware that I lack strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to make Emilia the ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make her wish come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:49.71,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not feel that your answer \Nis too arrogant by far?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:53.76,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Weakness is something to feel \Nshame, not pride, about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:58.21,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,To earn the right to stand here, \Nhave you worked hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:01.72,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Have you done enough service to shame us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Imperial Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:07.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still going to make Emilia the ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:10.24,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I fail to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:12.03,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,After being so denied,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why do you continue to stand here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:23.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's special!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:28.54,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I understand and accept your \Nreason for standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:33.82,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But I do not think I can \Nacknowledge you as a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:35.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:39.05,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who inspires such an expression
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:42.89,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,on the face of one they wish to \Nstand beside, cannot be a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:50.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is being a knight that big a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:52.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You just happened to be born into the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:54.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like a big-shot\Nwith your daddy's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:55.74,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.64,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,that is not a beautiful look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:06.83,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:11.88,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I am deeply sorry to waste your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.44,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I will make him stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:17.51,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:24.29,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,if nothing else, he has shown us all \Nthat you are not one to be feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.72,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,You have a fine attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:27.56,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:31.98,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,not my attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.78,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru-dono, please leave the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:49.87,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us discuss how the royal \Nselection will proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.96,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.26,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:04.93,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Rom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:13.74,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.32,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,but for stealing into\Nthe castle, you must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.81,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:20.53,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I cannot comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:22.75,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,You have publicly declared that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.12,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,you have no intention of participating \Nin the royal selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:30.98,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,I am not obligated to obey your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:39.46,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:42.64,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do your stupid royal selection!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.26,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to try to be\Nthe next ruler, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.97,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you sayin', Felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.47,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,That old man is my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.20,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,so release him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treat him with care!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:55.69,Default,Marcos,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.98,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Felt... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:02.45,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk later, Old Man Rom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.25,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Reinhard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:11.45,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,was this all part of your plan, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.16,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was something far greater, \Nguided by fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.30,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a slave to fate or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:20.96,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:24.80,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I am your knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.18,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:28.42,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:33.39,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Felt-sama and her knight, Reinhard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:38.06,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,may we conclude that you both intend \Nto participate in the royal selection?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.00,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me just say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.45,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the nobility!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.41,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I hate knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.87,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.50,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I hate everything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:56.71,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm planning to tear it all down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:58.84,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:01.84,Default,Rickert,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.99,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,If I become the next ruler,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy everything! I'll take \Ndown every last one of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:13.10,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,and bring a little fresh\Nair into this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:17.15,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,Your mistress is quite an intense lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:21.72,Default,Reingard,0000,0000,0000,,One day, Felt-sama's words \Nwill reach everyone's ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.19,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:28.16,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,all of the candidates are finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:33.94,Default,Miklotov,0000,0000,0000,,The royal selection will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:40.81,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the royal selection \Nhas finally begun, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:43.84,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-{\i1}kyun{\i0}, you're Emilia-sama's \Nknight {\i1}nyow{\i0}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.75,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:49.01,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for interrupting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.50,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you would not make \Nsuch an unpleasant face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.68,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to warmly welcome me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.61,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but if you take that attitude—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:06.46,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It will call into question the respectability \Nof those in your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:07.86,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Do be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:14.97,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you asked me why \NI was here, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.16,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.07,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.61,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Julius, you shouldn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:33.28,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,He insulted us, the knights, before the \Ncandidates to be our future ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:36.69,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And he mocked the chivalry we practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:40.22,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I admit that he said some \Nthings that went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:43.63,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,But for such a matter, he need \Nonly be warned and corrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:47.57,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is not only my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:49.68,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby administer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:53.03,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,the death penalty to this insubordinate man, \Nwho sullied the knighthood's honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:59.29,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, it wouldn't be unusual \Nfor you to be slain for insolence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:03.74,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,However, much to my dismay, \Nyou are Emilia-sama's attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:06.76,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we will fight using wooden swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:10.51,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'm not gonna hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:27.31,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you truly have no pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.32,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What a simple, vulgar way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.08,Default,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:41.41,Default,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Knights Julius and Natsuki Subaru-dono \Nare having a mock battle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.54,Default,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,with wooden swords in the training ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,How did that happen? I have to—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.30,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanna know one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:52.64,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of 'em issued the challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.90,Default,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told it was the knight Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:57.23,Default,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru-dono accepted,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leading to this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.52,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm against stopping them, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:06.03,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But your knight and my, \Num... friend are fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.67,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.50,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,Worried? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.07,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,That Julius will go too far,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll have to pay for your boy's treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.47,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,If it is a question of the mock battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.83,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot agree with stopping \Nit before they finish, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.18,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,If they're just duking it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.48,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,you could've waited until it ended \Nand told us who won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.13,Default,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am! But the fight was, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.44,Default,Knight,0000,0000,0000,,It was just so one-sided, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.51,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.91,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We should go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:37.85,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You like to watch vicious beasts torment \Nweak creatures, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:41.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misjudge me with your \Nunfounded imaginings, Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.23,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,But yes, I do love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:49.73,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you admit that you \Nhave reached your limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.26,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you have now realized, \Nto a painful extent,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:57.70,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,just what the knights that you insulted, \Nand made light of, really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:04.83,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I believe continuing would endanger your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:06.33,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.54,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll break...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.67,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,that nose of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.51,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.38,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.18,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.18,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Shamac!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:32.23,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This was the ace up your sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.62,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Your skill level is far too low.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:37.39,Default,JUlius,0000,0000,0000,,Such low-level magic
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will only work on unintelligent beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.70,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You are irredeemably powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.42,Default,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You are not worthy to stand at her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.54,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So I didn't die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:09.54,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That talk with the royal candidates...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:12.65,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:14.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's head straight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,We need to work out a plan for the selec—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.32,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.83,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:25.55,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I have some things I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:28.16,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:30.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:35.84,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you end up, well, fighting Julius?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:38.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,There must have been a reason, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:40.06,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, it must've been important—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:42.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:43.61,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:45.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I was being stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:48.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,He said I was pathetic, powerless, \Nand unworthy of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:53.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,He was trying to distance me \Nfrom you, and I hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:54.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I fought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:57.99,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:05.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia, you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.17,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:11.37,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Roswaal and I will return to \Nthe mansion tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:15.42,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You will stay in the capital to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.84,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that our agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.07,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But wait a—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:23.56,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You came to the capital so Felis \Ncould heal your exhausted gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:25.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you suddenly... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.40,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:33.44,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with you, you always push \Nyourself to do the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:37.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm saying... I just—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.05,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,"Just"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:43.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to do something for you, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:45.70,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:50.63,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It was for you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:54.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No... I just wanted to do something for you—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:03.22,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Stop telling lies about how \Neverything is for my sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:08.77,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Coming to the castle, \Nfighting Julius, using magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.98,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that was all for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:14.28,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I never asked you to do any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:19.11,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you remember\Nwhat I asked you to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:19.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:24.69,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to wait at the lodging with Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:29.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you not to use magic because \Nusing more would endanger you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:32.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't do as you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.79,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you're wrong. You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:37.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I... I didn't do it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:44.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You won't believe me, Emilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:45.56,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe you, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:50.16,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:54.69,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who won't \Ngive me a reason to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:59.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:05.15,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But just like that, you threw it away, \Nand came all the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.03,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You won't keep your promise to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:12.36,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,and you ask me to believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:14.87,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:19.32,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:24.27,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep trying to help me like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:27.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Because you helped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:31.13,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I... helped you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:32.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:36.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even realize
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how the things you've done \Nfor me have saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.90,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't expect you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:48.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true! You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:51.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So everything I've done has been to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:54.04,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:58.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you don't, but please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:00.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You were the...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came to this world, you were—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:10.80,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, you won't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:14.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:16.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:19.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,if anyone could understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:21.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:25.39,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,The version of me that lives within \Nyou must be amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:28.97,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,She can understand everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you don't explain it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:37.54,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,She can feel all your pain, sadness, \Nand anger as her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:43.08,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand if you\Ndon't tell me, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:47.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:51.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:56.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,haven't I made everything work out all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:00.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,When your insignia was stolen, I saved you \Nfrom an insane killer at the loot house!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:02.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I risked my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:04.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All because you were important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.83,0:23:06.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,At the mansion, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:07.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Things worked out because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:10.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Without me, it would've been a lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:12.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All of it, all of it, all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:15.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All of it was because I was there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.40,0:23:20.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You should have a greater debt to me \Nthan you could ever repay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:23.13,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:28.46,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you so many debts, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:32.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right! That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:35.72,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll repay all of them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:39.03,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:45.54,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You've done enough, Natsuki Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.94,0:23:49.78,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I had hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:53.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That only you wouldn't give \Nme special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:23:59.08,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That you'd look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:03.21,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,in the same, exact way you \Nlook at everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.30,0:24:06.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.40,0:24:11.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't look at you the way I look at others.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.19,0:24:13.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.82,0:24:35.82,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Self-Proclaimed Knight \NNatsuki {\c&H8B8B8E&}Su{\c&HFFFFFF&}baru
